snippet.title: The Elder Scrolls Online: Necrom Teaser | Xbox & Bethesda Developer Direct 2023
snippet.description:
The Elder Scrolls Online: Necrom includes a new playable class, and only the third new class since launch. The expansion takes place in Eastern Morrowind, and expands the world of Tamriel. ESO has no required subscription, and The Elder Scrolls Online: Necrom expansion releases June 5, 2023 to PC, and June 20, 2023 to XBox.

#xbox #eso #gaming
